text: Jordanoleiopus ugandicola is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1964.Biolib.cz - Jordanoleiopus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Polymistoleiopus Category:Beetles described in 1964 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
